  "title": "Marketing & Enrolment Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are seeking a driven and strategic Marketing & Enrolment Manager to lead student recruitment growth and strengthen our school’s brand presence. This role plays a critical front-facing and leadership function — engaging parents, managing the admissions journey, and delivering impactful marketing initiatives that translate directly into enrolments.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Lead the development and execution of targeted student recruitment strategies to increase enrolment numbers</li><li>Engage parents and prospective students through clear communication and relationship-building to enhance the admissions experience</li><li>Manage the end-to-end admissions process to ensure a seamless and positive journey for applicants</li><li>Design and implement marketing campaigns that effectively promote the school’s brand and value proposition</li><li>Analyze recruitment and marketing data to measure campaign effectiveness and inform continuous improvement</li><li>Collaborate with cross-functional teams to align marketing initiatives with overall school objectives and growth targets</li></ul>",
